data.description: This Ridgewood home is a true gem! There are 3 bedrooms and 1 1/2 bathrooms. The first floor includes an eat in kitchen, dining room and living room.  Enjoy the screened-in patio off of the living room, it is perfect for enjoying the outdoors. The second floor has 3 bedrooms and a large full bathroom. One of the unique features of this home is its finished attic with two bonus rooms for versatile space (approximately 300 additional square feet not included in the auditors amount). The basement provides tons of storage and a half bathroom.  The two- car detached garage and fenced backyard add further convenience and charm. Overall, this beautiful home in Ridgewood is the perfect blend of style, comfort, and functionality.
